msgid ""
"The next code snippet shows the XML configuration for a login use case. Note "
"that the `userService` bean has a dependency on a request-scoped "
"`loginAction` bean. Also, the `LoginAction` is instantiated by using "
"xref:core/expressions.adoc[SpEL expressions] that retrieve the username and "
"password from the current HTTP request. In our test, we want to configure "
"these request parameters through the mock managed by the TestContext "
"framework.  The following listing shows the configuration for this use case:"
msgstr ""

